.container
  = link_to 'All patterns', patterns_path
  - @patterns.each do |pattern|
    = link_to pattern.name, patterns_path(selected: pattern.id)

.container
  - if @selected_pattern
    = @selected_pattern.name
    pattern
    %div
      = @selected_pattern.description
  - else
    All patterns
    Kitsch banjo truffaut asymmetrical fingerstache brooklyn. Green juice artisan DIY wayfarers post-ironic fixie. Coloring book keytar vape kale chips trust fund. Artisan ennui food truck pinterest wolf art party master cleanse schlitz pabst. Vinyl fanny pack PBR&B activated charcoal shoreditch before they sold out venmo beard literally pickled. Cray salvia poke normcore vinyl XOXO. Crucifix stumptown celiac 3 wolf moon.

.container
  %table
    - @services.each do |service|
      %tr
        %td
          = service.name
        %td
          - service.patterns.each do |service_pattern|
            = service_pattern.name
